snippet.textDisplay:
It is so sad that great Amjad Sabri was assassinated by the Taliban in 2016, who considered his Qawali blasphemous. His songs/voice have clearly brought people closer to Islam and its philosophy of peace, even for non-muslims, like me. 

I googled to know more about Amjadji, only to be shocked on reading about his assassination. 

RIP 

Love from India
